sys_ui_script.script:
<!DOCTYPE html> <html lang="en-US" ng-app="snoff" ng-controller="MainCtrl"> <head> <title>ServiceNow Offline v{{application.version}} - {{application.name}}</title>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<!-- Load Bootstrap CSS --> <link rel="stylesheet" href="data:text/css;base64,">
<!-- Load jQuery --> <!-- <script src="./jquery.min.js"></script> --> <script src="data:application/javascript;base64,"></script>
<!-- Load Bootstrap --> <!-- <script src="./bootstrap.min.js"></script> --> <script src="data:application/javascript;base64,"></script>
<!-- Load AngularJS --> <!-- <script src="./angular.min.js"></script> --> <script src="data:application/javascript;base64,"></script>
<!-- Load AngularJS toArrayFilter - needed for sorting of Objects instead of Arrays in ng-repeat --> <!-- <script src="./angular-toArrayFilter.js"></script> --> <script src="data:application/javascript;base64,"></script>
<!-- ToDo: include this external code into the single file app --> <!-- Load custom Javascript Classes --> <!--<script src="./classes.js"></script> --> <script> // Shared functions & variables // ============================
function generateGUID() { return 'xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx'.replace(/[x]/g, function(c) { var num = Math.random() *16 | 0, v = c === 'x' ? num : (num&0x3|0x8); return v.toString(16); }); }
function findObjectInArray(arr, id) { for (var i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) { var obj = arr[i];
if (obj.id == id) { return i; // Return array index of found object } }
return -1; // Return -1 if object not found }
function findObjectNameInArray(arr, id) { for (var i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) { var obj = arr[i];
if (obj.name == id) { return i; // Return array index of found object } }
return -1; // Return -1 if object not found }
function loadDataFromObject(objTarget, objSource) { for (var prop in objSource) { switch (prop) { case 'metaData': // Do not allow these properties to be loaded from saved data break; default: if (typeof objTarget.metaData.fields[prop] !== 'undefined') { switch (objTarget.metaData.fields[prop].type) { case 'Reference': if (objSource[prop] != null) { eval('objTarget[prop] = new ' + objTarget.metaData.fields[prop].referenceClass + '(objSource[prop])'); } break; case 'Date': if (objSource[prop] != null) { eval('objTarget[prop] = new Date(objSource[prop])'); } break; case 'Array': objTarget[prop] = [];
for (var i = 0; i < objSource[prop].length; i++) { eval('objTarget[prop].push(new ' + objTarget.metaData.fields[prop].referenceClass + '(objSource[prop][i]))'); } break; default: objTarget[prop] = objSource[prop]; } } else { if (prop.substring(0, 3) != 'tmp') { // Exclude temporary variables objTarget[prop] = objSource[prop]; } } } }
if (objTarget.constructor.name == 'Application') { objTarget.tmpActivePage = 'main';
// ToDo: Fix the two lines below // objTarget.tmpEditRecord = new Transaction(); objTarget.tmpActiveObjectCollection = objTarget.transaction; } };
function Field(obj) { // Field class this.id = generateGUID(); this.active = true; this.metaData = { 'className': 'Field', 'collection': 'field', 'labelSingular': 'Field', 'labelPlural': 'Fields', 'labelInsert': null, 'labelUpdate': null, 'labelDelete': null, 'allowedOperations': { 'insert': false, 'read': true, 'update': false, 'delete': false }, 'fields': { 'name': { 'name': 'name', 'order': 10, 'type': 'String', 'required': true, 'maxChars': 100, 'labelSingular': 'field_name', 'labelPlural': 'field_names', 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false }, 'label': { 'name': 'label', 'order': 20, 'type': 'String', 'required': true, 'maxChars': 100, 'labelSingular': 'field_label', 'labelPlural': 'field_labels', 'showInList': true, 'showInForm': true }, 'type': { 'name': 'type', 'order': 30, 'type': 'String', 'required': true, 'maxChars': 100, 'labelSingular': 'field_type', 'labelPlural': 'field_types', 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false }, 'value': { 'name': 'value', 'order': 40, 'type': 'String', 'required': true, 'maxChars': 4000, 'labelSingular': 'field_value', 'labelPlural': 'field_values', 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false }, 'displayValue': { 'name': 'displayValue', 'order': 50, 'type': 'String', 'required': true, 'maxChars': 4000, 'labelSingular': 'field_display_value', 'labelPlural': 'field_display_values', 'showInList': true, 'showInForm': true } } }; this.name = null; this.label = null; this.type = null; this.value = null; this.displayValue = null;
if (typeof obj === 'object') { // If an object was passed then initialize properties from that object loadDataFromObject(this, obj); } }
function Record(obj) { // Record class this.id = generateGUID(); this.active = true; this.metaData = { 'className': 'Record', 'collection': 'record', 'labelSingular': 'Record', 'labelPlural': 'Records', 'labelInsert': 'Create New Record', 'labelUpdate': 'Edit Record', 'labelDelete': null, 'allowedOperations': { 'insert': true, 'read': true, 'update': true, 'delete': false }, 'fields': { 'sys_id': { 'name': 'sys_id', 'order': 10, 'type': 'String', 'required': false, 'maxChars': 40, 'labelSingular': 'record_sys_id', 'labelPlural': 'record_sys_ids', 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false }, 'displayValue': { 'name': 'displayValue', 'order': 20, 'type': 'String', 'required': false, 'maxChars': 1000, 'labelSingular': 'record_display_value', 'labelPlural': 'record_display_values', 'showInList': true, 'showInForm': true }, 'field': { 'name': 'field', 'order': 30, 'type': 'Array', 'referenceClass': 'Field', 'required': false, 'labelSingular': 'record_field', 'labelPlural': 'record_fields', 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false } } }; this.sys_id = null; this.displayValue = null; this.field = [];
if (typeof obj === 'object') { // If an object was passed then initialize properties from that object loadDataFromObject(this, obj); } }
function Table(obj) { // Table class this.id = generateGUID(); this.active = true; this.metaData = { 'className': 'Table', 'collection': 'table', 'labelSingular': 'Table', 'labelPlural': 'Tables', 'labelInsert': null, 'labelUpdate': 'Edit Table', 'labelDelete': null, 'allowedOperations': { 'insert': false, 'read': true, 'update': true, 'delete': false }, 'fields': { 'name': { 'name': 'name', 'order': 10, 'type': 'String', 'required': false, 'maxChars': 100, 'labelSingular': 'table_name', 'labelPlural': 'table_names', 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false }, 'label': { 'name': 'label', 'order': 20, 'type': 'String', 'required': false, 'maxChars': 100, 'labelSingular': 'table_label', 'labelPlural': 'table_labels', 'showInList': true, 'showInForm': true }, 'record': { 'name': 'record', 'order': 30, 'type': 'Array', 'referenceClass': 'Record', 'required': false, 'labelSingular': 'table_record', 'labelPlural': 'table_records', 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false } } }; this.name = null; this.label = null; this.record = [];
if (typeof obj === 'object') { // If an object was passed then initialize properties from that object loadDataFromObject(this, obj); } }
// ServiceNow genereated information var CONSTARRAYTABLE = '***SNOFF***'; // =================================
function Application(obj) { // Application (Main) class // Variables this.id = generateGUID(); this.active = true; this.metaData = { 'className': 'Application', 'fields': { 'name': { 'name': 'name', 'order': 10, 'type': 'String', 'required': true, 'maxChars': 100, 'labelSingular': 'name', 'labelPlural': null, 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false }, 'version': { 'name': 'version', 'order': 20, 'type': 'String', 'required': true, 'maxChars': 100, 'labelSingular': null, 'labelPlural': null, 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false }, 'instanceName': { 'name': 'instanceName', 'order': 30, 'type': 'string', 'required': false, 'labelSingular': 'instance_name', 'labelPlural': null, 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false }, 'instanceUsername': { 'name': 'instanceUsername', 'order': 40, 'type': 'string', 'required': false, 'labelSingular': 'instance_username', 'labelPlural': null, 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false }, 'instancePassword': { 'name': 'instancePassword', 'order': 50, 'type': 'string', 'required': false, 'labelSingular': 'instance_password', 'labelPlural': null, 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false }, 'debugMode': { 'name': 'debugMode', 'order': 60, 'type': 'Boolean', 'required': false, 'labelSingular': 'debug_mode', 'labelPlural': null, 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false }, 'table': { 'name': 'table', 'order': 130, 'type': 'Array', 'referenceClass': 'Table', 'required': false, 'labelSingular': 'table', 'labelPlural': 'tables', 'showInList': false, 'showInForm': false } } }; this.name = 'ToDo: Info from SNC'; this.version = '1.0'; this.instanceName = null; this.instanceUsername = null; this.instancePassword =null; this.debugMode = false; this.table = CONSTARRAYTABLE; this.tmpActivePage = 'main'; this.tmpTableIndex = -1;
// ToDo: Fix the two lines below this.tmpActiveObjectCollection = this.table; this.tmpEditRecord = new Table();
this.setActivePage = function (activePage) { this.tmpActivePage = activePage;
switch (activePage.split('_')[0]) { case 'main': this.tmpEditRecord = new Table(); this.tmpActiveObjectCollection = this.table; break; case 'table': var result = $.grep(this.table, function(e){ return e.name == activePage.split('_')[1]; }); if (result.length == 1) { this.tmpActiveObjectCollection = this.table[findObjectNameInArray(this.table, activePage.split('_')[1])]; this.tmpTableIndex = findObjectNameInArray(this.table, activePage.split('_')[1]); this.tmpEditRecord = new Record(); } else { // ToDo: Fix the line below this.tmpActiveObjectCollection = this.table; this.tmpEditRecord = new Table(); } break; default: this.tmpEditRecord = new Table(); tmpActiveObjectCollection = this.table; } };
this.editRecord = function (recordId, recordClass, table) { eval('this.tmpEditRecord = new Record()'); eval('var tmpArray = this.table[' + this.tmpTableIndex + '].record');
if (recordId != 'new') { var tmpIndex = findObjectInArray(tmpArray, recordId); if (tmpIndex != -1) { loadDataFromObject(this.tmpEditRecord, tmpArray[tmpIndex]); $("#modalEditRecord").modal('show'); } else { // This situation should not be possible to reach log('Error: System tried to edit a ' + recordClass + ', but the ' + recordClass + ' is no longer in the ' + recordClass + '-array. ' + recordClass + ' ID = ' + recordId + '.'); log(tmpArray); } } else { $("#modalEditRecord").modal('show'); } };
this.saveRecord = function () { eval('var tmpArray = this.table[' + this.tmpTableIndex + '].record');
// Calculate all Number-fields; transform input-field to calculated value for (var field in this.tmpEditRecord.fields) { if (this.tmpEditRecord.fields[field].type == 'Number') { // ToDo: Check Number Input field for valid math expression and that the result is a number. Also select number of decimals to show (property?) // ToDo: Use regular expression to ensure that it is a valid math expression (allowing +, -, * and / only and parentecis) // ToDo: Use eval to execute the expression. this.tmpEditRecord[this.tmpEditRecord.metaData.fields[field].name] = this.tmpEditRecord[this.tmpEditRecord.metaData.fields[field].name + 'Input'] = eval(this.tmpEditRecord[this.tmpEditRecord.metaData.fields[field].name + 'Input']); } } };
if (typeof obj === 'object') { // If an object was passed then initialize properties from that object loadDataFromObject(this, obj); } } </script>
<!-- ToDo: include this external code into the single file app --> <!-- Load AngularJS Controllers --> <!--<script src="./angularjs_controllers.js"></script>--> <script> var app = angular.module('snoff', ['angular-toArrayFilter']);
app.controller('MainCtrl', function($scope, $http, $filter) { $http.defaults.headers.common['Authorization'] = 'Basic ' + window.btoa('lars-ake.bolk@soprasteria.com:9rIat5oEjo'); // ToDo - use settingsfields!!! $http.defaults.headers.common['Access-Control-Allow-Origin'] = "*"; $http.defaults.headers.common['Access-Control-Allow-Headers'] = "X-Requested-With";
$scope.application = new Application(); $scope.online = navigator.onLine;
$scope.changeOnlineStatus = function() { $scope.$apply(function () { $scope.online = navigator.onLine; }); };
window.addEventListener('online', $scope.changeOnlineStatus); window.addEventListener('offline', $scope.changeOnlineStatus);
if (localStorage.getItem('SNOff') !== null) { $scope.application = new Application(JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('SNOff'))); }
$scope.$watchCollection( 'application', function (newValue, oldValue) { $scope.saveApplication(false); } );
$scope.saveApplication = function(feedBack) { localStorage.setItem('SNOff', JSON.stringify($scope.application));
$scope.log('Application Object saved to Local Storage.'); };
$scope.synchData = function () { alert('Hello World');
// POST r insert, PUT r update
// 1. Loopa igenom alla tabeller
// Fr varje tabell loopa igenom alla poster
// Fr varje post abgr om det r en insert eller en update
// Gr REST POST/PUT
$.ajax ({ type: "PUT", url: "https://dev13355.service-now.com/api/now/table/incident/47064b68a9fe19810186793eefffc9b7?sysparm_display_value=false&sysparm_exclude_reference_link=true&sysparm_fields=sys_id%2Cnumber", contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8", dataType: 'json', async: true, beforeSend: function (xhr) { xhr.setRequestHeader ("Authorization", "Basic " + btoa('lars-ake.bolk@soprasteria.com' + ":" + '9rIat5oEjo')); }, data: '{"short_description":"qwerty"}', success: function (response){ console.log(response); alert('Thanks for your comment!'); }, error: function (jqXHR, status) { console.log(jqXHR); console.log(status); alert('Failure'); } });
// Spara resultatet fr varje POST/PUT
// Visa resultatsida dr alla misslyckade poster listas, med klickbara lnkar fr att kunna uppdatera respektive post. }
$scope.log = function(logObject) { if ($scope.application.debugMode) { console.log(logObject); } };
// Functions for development purposes - only available to user when Debug Mode is on // ================================================================================= $scope.clearLocalStorage = function() { // ToDo: Temporary localStorage-clear-function - remove/rewrite localStorage.clear();
$scope.log('Application Object cleared from Local Storage.'); };
$scope.invertBoolean = function(obj) { obj.active = !obj.active; $scope.saveApplication(); } }); </script> </head>
<body> <!-- Navbar --> <nav class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top"> <div class="container-fluid"> <div class="navbar-header"> <ul class="nav navbar-nav"> <li class="dropdown" style="display: inline-block;"> <a class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" href="#"> ServiceNow Offline - {{application.name}} </a> <ul class="dropdown-menu"> <li> <a data-toggle="tab" href="#main" ng-click="application.setActivePage('main')"> Start </a> </li> <li role="separator" class="divider"></li> <li class="dropdown-header">Tables</li> <li ng-repeat="table in application.table"> <a data-toggle="tab" href="#table_{{table.name}}" ng-click="application.setActivePage('table_' + table.name)"> {{table.label}} </a> </li> <li role="separator" class="divider" ng-show="application.debugMode"></li> <li class="dropdown-header" ng-show="application.debugMode">System Test Functions</li> <li ng-show="application.debugMode"> <a data-toggle="tab" href="#" ng-click="saveApplication(true)"> Save </a> </li> <li ng-show="application.debugMode"> <a data-toggle="tab" href="#" ng-click="clearLocalStorage()"> Clear LocalStorage </a> </li> </ul> </li> <li style="display: inline-block;"> <a data-toggle="tab" href="#settings" ng-click="application.setActivePage('settings')"> Settings </a> </li> <li style="display: inline-block;"> <button class="btn btn-success" ng-click="synchData()" ng-disabled="!online"> Upload </button> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </nav>
<!-- Tab Content --> <div class="container-fluid" style="margin-top: 55px;"> <div class="tab-content"> <div id="main" class="tab-pane fade in active"> <h3>ServiceNow Offline - Start</h3> </div>
<div id="{{application.tmpActivePage}}" class="tab-pane fade in"> <h3 ng-show="application.tmpActivePage == 'settings'">Settings</h3> <h3 ng-hide="application.tmpActivePage == 'settings'">{{application.tmpEditRecord.metaData.labelPlural}}</h3>
<form ng-show="application.tmpActivePage == 'settings'" novalidate role="form"> <div class="form-group"> <label for="applicationInstanceName">Instance Name</label> <input type="text" class="form-control" id="applicationInstanceName" ng-model="application.instanceName" placeholder="Enter instancename" ng-maxlength="100" /> </div>
<div class="form-group"> <label for="applicationInstanceUsername">Username</label> <input type="text" class="form-control" id="applicationInstanceUsername" ng-model="application.instanceUsername" placeholder="Enter username" ng-maxlength="100" /> </div>
<div class="form-group"> <label for="applicationInstancePassword">Password</label> <input type="password" class="form-control" id="applicationInstancePassword" ng-model="application.instancePassword" placeholder="Enter password" ng-maxlength="100" /> </div>
<div class="checkbox"> <label> <input type="checkbox" id="applicationDebugMode" ng-model="application.debugMode" value="" />Debug Mode </label> </div> </form>
<span ng-hide="application.tmpActivePage == 'settings'"> <button class="btn btn-success" ng-show="application.tmpEditRecord.metaData.allowedOperations.insert" ng-click="application.editRecord('new', application.tmpEditRecord.metaData.className)"> Create New Record </button>
<div class="row"> <div type="button" class="btn btn-info col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3" style="margin: 5px; width: 350px; height: 350px; text-align: left; opacity: {{record.active?1.0:0.5}}" ng-repeat="record in application.tmpActiveObjectCollection.record"> <!-- [General Top] --> <span ng-show="record.metaData.allowedOperations.activate" ng-click="invertBoolean(record)"> <span ng-show="record.active">Active</span> <span style="color: silver;" ng-hide="record.active">Active</span>   <!-- ToDo: Maybe this glyphicon can be used instead of active-checkbok for layout purposes. A toggle-function must be written anyway sincechanges to the checkbo are not detected by the autosave-function --> </span> <span ng-show="record.metaData.allowedOperations.update" ng-click="application.editRecord(record.id, record.metaData.className)"></span>  <span ng-show="record.metaData.allowedOperations.delete" ng-click="application.removeRecordConfirm(record.id, record.metaData.className)"></span>
<h4><span class="no-overflow" ng-click="application.editRecord(record.id, record.metaData.className)">{{record.displayValue}}</span></h4> <hr /> <!-- <span ng-if="field.showInList" ng-repeat="field in record.field | toArray | orderBy : 'order'"> --> <span ng-if="field.showInList" ng-repeat="field in record.field"> <!-- String --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'XXXstring'"> <span class="no-overflow"><strong>{{field.label}}:</strong><br />{{record[field.value]}}</span> </span>
<!-- Date --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'glide_date'"> <span class="no-overflow"><strong>{{field.label}}:</strong><br />{{record[field.value] | date : "shortDate"}}</span> </span>
<!-- Reference --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'reference'"> <span class="no-overflow"><strong>{{field.label}}:</strong><br />{{record[field.value]}}</span> </span>
<!-- Number --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'decimal'"> <span class="no-overflow"><strong>{{field.label}}:</strong><br />{{record[field.value]}}</span> </span>
<!-- Text --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'string'"> <span class="no-overflow"><strong>{{field.label}}:</strong><br />{{record[field.value]}}</span> </span>
<!-- Url --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'url'"> <span class="no-overflow"><strong>{{field.label}}:</strong><br /><a href="{{record[field.value]}}" target="_blank" alt="{{field.label}}">{{record[field.value]}}</a></span> </span>
<!-- Boolean --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'boolean'"> <span class="no-overflow"><strong>{{field.label}}:</strong><br />ToDo: Display boolean value</span> </span> </span>
<!-- [General Bottom] --> </div> </div>
<button class="btn btn-success" ng-show="application.tmpEditRecord.metaData.allowedOperations.insert && application.tmpActiveObjectCollection.length > 3" ng-click="application.editRecord('new', application.tmpEditRecord.metaData.className)"> <span class="glyphicon {{application.tmpEditRecord.metaData.glyphicon}}" ng-show="application.tmpEditRecord.metaData.glyphicon"></span>{{application.getLabel(application.tmpEditRecord.metaData.labelInsert)}} </button> </span> </div> </div> </div>
<!-- Confirm Dialog --> <div id="modalConfirm" class="modal fade"> <div class="modal-dialog modal-sm"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">×</button> <h4 class="modal-title">{{application.getLabel('confirm')}}</h4> </div> <div class="modal-body"> <p>{{application.getLabel('confirm_remove')}}</p> <p class="text-warning"><small>---------ToDo: Optional warning text---------</small></p> </div> <div class="modal-footer"> <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">{{application.getLabel('no')}}</button> <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" ng-click="application.removeRecord()">{{application.getLabel('yes')}}</button> </div> </div> </div> </div>
<!-- Edit Record --> <!-- ToDo: This modal window must probably be able to distinguish between create and edit operations... --> <div id="modalEditRecord" class="modal fade"> <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">×</button> <h4 class="modal-title"><span class="glyphicon {{application.tmpEditRecord.metaData.glyphicon}}"></span> {{application.tmpEditRecord.metaData.labelPlural}}</h4> </div> <div class="modal-body"> <p>{{application.tmpEditRecord.metaData.labelPlural}}</p> <!-- ToDo: The title could be made better. --> <p class="text-warning"><small>---------ToDo: Optional info/warning text---------</small></p>
<form class="form-horizontal" name="inputForm" novalidate> <span ng-repeat="field in application.tmpEditRecord.metaData.fields | toArray | orderBy : 'order'"> <div class="form-group" ng-show="field.showInForm"> <label class="col-sm-2 control-label">{{application.getLabel(field.labelSingular)}}:</label> <div class="col-sm-10"> <!-- String --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'String'"> <div class="input-group"> <span ng-if="field.name == 'startBalanceInput'" class="input-group-addon">{{application.tmpEditRecord.currency.symbol}}</span> <input type="text" class="form-control" name="{{field.name}}" ng-model="application.tmpEditRecord[field.name]" placeholder="{{application.getLabel(field.labelSingular)}}" ng-maxlength="field.maxChars" ng-required="field.required" /> </div> </span> <!-- Date --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'Date'"> <div class="input-group"> <input type="date" class="form-control" name="{{field.name}}" ng-model="application.tmpEditRecord[field.name]" ng-required="field.required" /> </div> </span> <!-- Reference --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'Reference'"> <select name="{{field.name}}" class="form-control" ng-if="field.name != 'from' && field.name != 'to'" ng-model="application.tmpEditRecord[field.name]" ng-options="value.getName(application.currentLanguage) for value in application[field.collection] | filter: {active: true} track by value.id" ng-required="field.required"></select> <select name="{{field.name}}" class="form-control" ng-if="field.name == 'from'" ng-model="application.tmpEditRecord[field.name]" ng-options="value.getName(application.currentLanguage) for value in application[field.collection] | filter: filterFrom track by value.id" ng-required="field.required"> <option value="">-- Choose --</option> <!-- ToDo: Translate --> </select> <select name="{{field.name}}" class="form-control" ng-if="field.name == 'to'" ng-model="application.tmpEditRecord[field.name]" ng-options="value.getName(application.currentLanguage) for value in application[field.collection] | filter: filterTo track by value.id" ng-required="field.required"> <option value="">-- Choose --</option> <!-- ToDo: Translate --> </select> </span> <!-- Number --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'Number'"> <div class="input-group"> <input type="text" class="form-control" name="{{field.name}}" ng-model="application.tmpEditRecord[field.name]" placeholder="{{application.getLabel(field.labelSingular)}}" ng-maxlength="field.maxChars" ng-required="field.required" /> </div> </span>
<!-- Text --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'Text'"> <div class="input-group"> <textarea name="{{field.name}}" class="form-control" rows="5" ng-model="application.tmpEditRecord[field.name]" ng-maxlength="field.maxChars"></textarea> </div> </span>
<!-- Url --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'Url'"> <div class="input-group"> <input type="url" class="form-control" name="{{field.name}}" ng-model="application.tmpEditRecord[field.name]" placeholder="{{application.getLabel(field.labelSingular)}}" ng-maxlength="field.maxChars" ng-required="field.required" /> </div> </span>
<!-- Boolean --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'Boolean'"> <div class="input-group"> ToDo: create input object for boolean fields </div> </span>
<!-- Radio --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'Radio'"> <div class="input-group"> <div class="btn-group"> <span ng-repeat="value in field.values | toArray"> <label class="btn btn-default"> <input type="radio" name="{{field.name}}" value="{{value.value}}" ng-model="application.tmpEditRecord[field.name]" ng-required="{{field.required}}" /> {{value.label[application.currentLanguage.id]}} </label> </span> </div> </div> </span>
<!-- Tag --> <span ng-if="field.type == 'Tag'"> <tags-input name="{{field.name}}" ng-model="application.tmpEditRecord[field.name]" display-property="name" key-property="id" add-on-paste="true" placeholder="{{field.labelPlural}}" min-length="{{field.minTagLength}}" max-length="{{field.maxTagLength}}" min-tags="{{field.minTagNum}}" max-tags="{{field.maxTagNum}}" add-on-blur="false" on-tag-adding="addTag($tag)" replace-spaces-with-dashes="false" ng-required="{{field.required}}"> <auto-complete source="queryTags($query, false)" min-length="0" load-on-focus="true" load-on-empty="true" max-results-to-show="15" /> </tags-input> </span>
<div ng-messages="inputForm[field.name].$error" class="errors"> <span ng-message="required">{{application.getLabel('required')}}!</span> <span ng-message="maxlength">{{application.getLabel('maxlength')}}!</span> <span ng-message="url">{{application.getLabel('url_error')}}!</span> </div> </div> </div> </span> </form> </div> <div class="modal-footer"> <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">{{application.getLabel('cancel')}}</button> <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" ng-disabled="!inputForm.$valid" ng-click="application.saveRecord()"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-save"></span> {{application.getLabel('save')}}</button> <!-- ToDo: Also do the corresponding server side validation (how?). --> </div> </div> </div> </div>
